  &lt;li&gt;Click on the SCM icon in the sidebar. Validate that what was the single line commit message text box at the top has expanded to contain the non-comment template lines, and blank lines wherever there was a comment. Hmmm‚Ä¶ Wonder how we can have only non-comment lines from the template in the SCM editor‚Äôs commit text box, yet have the full template text at just a keystroke away if needed for reference  ToDo: Figure that out.&lt;/li&gt;
